# 7) `webui/systemd/uptimerobot-heartbeat-webui.service`

```ini
[Unit]
Description=5echo UptimeRobot Heartbeat Web UI
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=www-data
WorkingDirectory=/opt/uptimerobot-heartbeat/webui
Environment=WEBUI_USER=admin
Environment=WEBUI_PASS=change-me
ExecStart=/opt/uptimerobot-heartbeat/webui/.venv/bin/python /opt/uptimerobot-heartbeat/webui/app.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=3

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
